title: Dangerous Dungeon Escape
description: Dangerous Dungeon Escape, 던전 탈출이 너무 힘들다, Dungeon Escape is Very Hard, Too Difficult to Escape the Dungeon Go Insung did not pass onto hell or heaven after suddenly dying, but instead onto a dungeon. A place in between the afterlife and the world. And it’s no normal dungeon, but one with a system.While being watched by the numerous dead of the afterlife, Go Insung has to clear the dungeon with the other challengers in order to escape.
